spanishExample: ¡Recuerda lo que te dije! Por eso no lo encuentran.
englishTranslation: Remember what I told you! That’s why they don’t find it.

spanishExample: ¿Puedes recordarlo? Lo tenemos que encontrar.
englishTranslation: Can you remember it? We have to find it.

spanishExample: ¿Recuerdas dónde lo encontré? Dile esto a tu novio.
englishTranslation: Do you remember where I found it? Tell this to your boyfriend.

spanishExample: Encontraré a la niña con su abuelo.
englishTranslation: I’ll find the little girl with her grandfather.

spanishExample: Encontraremos lo que tu marido no ha encontrado.
englishTranslation: We’ll find what your husband hasn’t found.

spanishExample: Es humano, es posible que no lo encuentre.
englishTranslation: He’s human, it’s possible that he doesn’t find it.

spanishExample: Esa mujer te va a recordar a tu abuela.
englishTranslation: That woman is going to remind you of your grandmother.

spanishExample: Esos animales me recuerdan a mis días en el campo.
englishTranslation: Those animals remind me of my days in the country.

spanishExample: Le recordaré a tu tío que tiene que ir.
englishTranslation: I’ll remind your uncle that he has to go.

spanishExample: Necesitamos que él recuerde lo que pasó.
englishTranslation: We need him to remember what happened.

spanishExample: No creo que esa persona le recuerde a su tía.
englishTranslation: I don’t think that person reminds him of his aunt.

spanishExample: No encuentra la comida y quiere que yo la encuentre.
englishTranslation: He doesn’t find the food and he wants me to find it.

spanishExample: No estoy seguro de que esas personas le recuerden a sus padres.
englishTranslation: I’m not sure(m) those people remind her of her parents.

spanishExample: No la encontró y por eso queremos que ustedes la encuentren.
englishTranslation: He didn’t find her and that’s why we want you all to find her.

spanishExample: No lo encontraron y tampoco recuerdo dónde está.
englishTranslation: They didn’t find it and I don’t remember where it is either.

spanishExample: No lo encontraste, pero sé que ella lo encontrará.
englishTranslation: You didn't find it, but I know she’ll find it.

spanishExample: Nos encontramos con su enemigo cuando vamos a ese lugar.
englishTranslation: We come across her enemy when we go to that place.

spanishExample: Nos encontramos con su novia cerca de esa casa blanca.
englishTranslation: We came across her girlfriend near that white house.

spanishExample: Nunca lo encuentro aquí. Necesito tu ayuda para encontrarlo.
englishTranslation: I never find it here. I need your help in order to find it.

spanishExample: Por favor, encuentra lo que te dieron. Sé que lo encontrarás.
englishTranslation: Please, find what they gave you. I know you’ll find it.

spanishExample: Sé que te encuentras con ella en ese lugar.
englishTranslation: I know you come across her in that place.

spanishExample: Su novia me recuerda a una amiga.
englishTranslation: Her girlfriend reminds me of a friend.

spanishExample: Vamos a hacerlo para que recuerdes esas cosas.
englishTranslation: We’re going to do it so that you remember those things.
